body_html:
I have a question about caffe2 and tensorrt.

According to nvidia forum, Jetson 2 is not supporting tensorrt4 yet, it only support tensorrt3 for now(2018.6.15). Also, tensorrt3 is not supporting caffe2.
What is the advantage building with tensorrt3?

Thank you!
